
Generate a new component (it will prepend the name with 'app-'):
ng generate component <component_name> --style less


Open app:
ng serve
ng serve --port <port> (eg. 4200 or 4100)
ng serve --host <ip> --port <port>

eg.
ng serve --port 4100
ng serve --host 192.168.0.107 --port 4100


Build the app:
ng build

(Copy sources inside 'dist' folder and put them on the server)


Generate a new class

ng generate class <class_name>